{"tid":574133,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中央肥胖可以點解決?","createTime":"2018-02-27T06:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T11:04:31.000Z","uid":125903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3e30dc7101ec87ddde4544483f1f59c75a297e","tid":574133,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"通常一個星期做4次gym, 分別操手/肩/背/胸,操40分鐘,操完後就會係跑步機跑20分鐘(7km/h)<br />\n<br />\n但做落好似效果不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇爸打可以教我應該點做?<br />\n<br />\nThanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d4c1a7232997fa7f448b8ebfe63fa8b16b6ede","tid":574133,"uid":2333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"肥埋下半身先 變全體肥胖<br />\n再減就ok"},{"pid":"f59ab6ede1e8d69fdc3695f9f58de55c3c1632ac","tid":574133,"uid":28503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:40:59.000Z","msg":"練核心肌肉 帶氧"},{"pid":"9fb3fb4ceac5aa8bfb3754e2ffb68e16e7eaceca","tid":574133,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"冇，脂肪分佈同數量係你發育後已經定死左。<br />\n男士脂肪細胞大多係肚<br />\n女士係胸同臀部"},{"pid":"15bad9c6e603680f560a9fbe908a2e48175ad5a7","tid":574133,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"戒糖同節食，2個月包有效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0535b55dae64bc073fe82b6fad725ef74f11908","tid":574133,"uid":53443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9fb3fb4ceac5aa8bfb3754e2ffb68e16e7eaceca","tid":574133,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"冇，脂肪分佈同數量係你發育後已經定死左。<br />\n男士脂肪細胞大多係肚<br />\n女士係胸同臀部"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"一睇就知你係死肥撚<br />\n最鐘意搵籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8925f5fe529beeceed63c3f194ae958433dd6640","tid":574133,"ui